snippet.textDisplay:
Today(5th June) is my mother's birthday. Tomorrow (6th June) is my parents wedding anniversary.27th June is my father's death anniversary . And 30th June is my mother's death anniversary.😭😭😭 Aaj bhi yaad h, bachpan m Maine ekbar mummy papa ko bola tha, wow apka birthday aur anniversary June m aata h aur mumma n mzk m bola tha marungi bhi June m hi. Ye likhte waqt mera kaleja fata ja rha h. Zubaan pr saraswati ji baithi thi unke ya I don't know unko intuitiona aane lge the. 25th June ka mummy papa ka accident hua uske kuch din pehle hi mumma n mujhse mzk m bola tha m mar jaungi to reh Lena aaram s, aur dono choti behno ka bhi dhyaan rkhna. Aur sach m vo sab ho gya. Aaj 17 years ho gye unko gye, hum teenon sisters ki shadi bhi ho gyi par Aaj bhi, mummy papa ko bhool nhi paayi hu. Bahut yaad aati h mummaaa...plz come back plzz. I love you mummy papa. Aap jaha bhi ho pkka sath honge aur khush honge. 
Aansu rukte nhi h
Yaad jaati nhi h
Jo ek bar gye vo Laut k aate nhi h.
Ye song daily sunti hu aur ro leti hu. Guys pl respect your parents, give them time. Ye waqt fir nhi aayega, sirf pachtawa reh jayega. Aisa lgta h kaash Maine unhe jaane s rok liya hota. Mere school function ki dress lene gye the😭😭😭😭 M khud ko kbhi maaf nhi kr paungi. Aisa lgta h sab meri wajah s huaa.....Iam sorry mumma papa. I Love you bahut saaaraaaaa
